  "title": "Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role & Responsibilities</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Work with fund or security issuer on the subscription and redemption of funds or securities</li><li>Work with fund or security issuer to process the entitlement distribution as well as any capital call</li><li>Work with service providers or IRAS on withholding tax calculation, e-filing and payment processing</li><li>Closely monitor distribution pay-out from underlying base asset or funds</li><li>Perform account reconciliation</li><li>Perform regulatory reporting</li><li>Perform post trade settlement and product lifecycle management</li><li>Set up issuer fee schedule, monitor and follow up on due fee invoice payment for direct and third-party security token issuances</li><li>Maintain promotional campaigns on the ADDX proprietary platform</li><li>Assist in digitalizing workflows using an automation platform</li></ul><p><strong>Skills, Knowledge and/or Certifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Excel</li><li>Working knowledge of programming languages, such as SQL and Python, for data manipulation and automation. (<strong>Hard requirement</strong>)</li><li>Basic understanding of financial markets, including key concepts and terminology.</li><li>Strong attention to detail</li></ul>",
